title: Leading telecommunication companies in Norway 2019 , by turnover
summary: This is a bar chart. It shows Turnover in million NOK for 20 number of Telecom Names.
Telecom Name Telenor ASA has the highest Turnover in million NOK and Netel AS has the lowest Turnover in million NOK.
The Turnover in million NOK of Telecom Name Telenor ASA is 256.7% larger than the minimum value at Netel AS.
min_summary: This bar chart has 20 columns on the x axis representing Telecom Name, and Turnover in million NOK in each Telecom Name on the y axis.
The Turnover in million NOK is appeared to be the highest at Telecom Name Telenor ASA and lowest at Telecom Name Netel AS.

max_summary: This bar chart has 20 columns on the x axis representing Telecom Name, and Turnover in million NOK in each Telecom Name on the y axis.
The Turnover in million NOK is highest at Telecom Name Telenor ASA and lowest at Telecom Name Netel AS.
Second maximum Turnover in million NOK is found at Telecom Name Telenor Norge AS.
Telecom Name Netel AS has 256.7 times less Turnover in million NOK than Telecom Name Telenor ASA which is the highest.
Turnover in million NOK at Telecom Name Telenor ASA is 124756.0 , second place is Telenor Norge AS at 24669.0, and thirdly is Telia Norge AS at 9091.0.
Considered together, the average Turnover in million NOK in all 20 Telecom Names is roughly 9109.45.
The Turnover in million NOK is 182189.0 if we add up values of all Telecom Names.
